public class TestPhone
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements PhoneListener, RawPhone

This is a simple implementation of RawPhone that provides a GUI interface. Currently simple calls may be made, received and disconnected. MVC is not currently implemented, but should be. Creation date: (2000-02-07 14:03:01)
